@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ximtgj(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.74 + (0.94 + wp.sin(v1 + 0.70)))
    tmp = wp.exp((wp.exp(v1 + 0.98) + tmp))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.31 - v0 + 0.43)) / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.63) / (v1 + 0.34 * v2 + 0.99)))
    v0 = wp.abs((0.95 / v0))
    tmp = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.25 - tmp + 0.35) / (v0 + 0.72 - v0 + 0.52)))
    data[tid] = v0
